---
name: leadbay_import_status
kind: tool-description
short_description: |
  Retrieve the current state of an async lead import by `handle_id`
  (or legacy `importIds[]`). Single refresh pass — never polls in a loop.
annotations:
  readOnlyHint: true
  destructiveHint: false
  idempotentHint: true
