---
Retrieve the current state of an async lead import. Pass `handle_id` returned by `leadbay_import_leads({wait_for_completion:false})`, or pass legacy `importIds[]` to inspect backend wizard rows. This status call performs a single refresh pass and never polls in a loop.

{{include:headers/tool-when-to-use}} after leadbay_import_leads or leadbay_import_and_qualify returns `{status:'running', handle_id}` for the import phase, call this tool later to retrieve progress or the final import result without re-running the import.

{{include:headers/tool-when-not-to-use}} for qualification handles returned as `qualify_id` — use leadbay_qualify_status for those; or when you still want the legacy blocking behavior from leadbay_import_leads with `wait_for_completion=true`.
